      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine and transmission operate smoothly, providing a reliable driving experience. The interior is clean with only minor signs of wear, and the exterior paint retains a nice shine, though there are a few small, typical stone chips from regular use. All major systems are functioning as they should, making this a solid choice for anyone looking for a dependable pre-owned vehicle.",
