    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been meticulously maintained by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts without hesitation, and all major electronic features are fully functional. Inside, the cabin remains clean and smoke-free, though you may find minor surface wear consistent with careful use. While the exterior paint still holds a great shine, there are a few very light scratches and one small stone chip on the hood that do not detract from its overall sharp appearance. This is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner with no immediate repairs needed.",
