      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This car is an absolute dream and has been my pride and joy. It's in truly pristine condition\u2014spotless inside and out, garage-kept, and drives like a cloud! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it just as much. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
