    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offering a definitive 1988 Porsche 911 Carrera, featuring the highly sought-after G50 Getrag 5-speed manual transaxle and a numbers-matching 3.2L air-cooled flat-six. This example boasts a dry undercarriage with zero seepage at the case halves or valve covers. The Bosch Motronic DME fuel injection provides a linear power band, while a recent top-end refresh ensures factory-spec compression and leak-down numbers. The suspension is dialed in with Bilstein dampers and original torsion bars, maintaining perfect chassis geometry. Riding on staggered 16-inch Fuchs forged alloys with N-rated tires, this vehicle exhibits crisp synchro engagement and precise steering rack feedback. A concours-level specimen with a comprehensive service dossier and all original VIN stickers intact.",
      "price": 44500.0,
