      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a rare, collector-grade specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in an exterior with deep, mirror-like paint clarity and zero stone chips or swirl marks. The finish is further protected by a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of perfection; the leather remains supple and matte with no bolster wear, and all interior surfaces are free of scratches or UV fading. Every electronic component and switch functions with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is peerless, boasting a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule at authorized facilities. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its pampered life. Included are all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a detailed binder of service records. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously curated piece of automotive history for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
